metadata.name: #10K #1/100
metadata.description:
"This is a bold community being created to reward the holders of the first #10k Inscription and unite the projects under this number.  
This NFT will be able to get an Inscription in the near future and it will be essential to be part of the community."  
The first batch is 1000. So think this as a key of an exclusive community in the near future.
